01:13:40.666 --> 01:13:42.168
<i>I started taking CDs</i>

01:13:42.251 --> 01:13:43.604
<i>and things like that
for him to listen to,</i>

01:13:43.628 --> 01:13:45.551
<i>to fill in the time a bit,</i>

01:13:45.630 --> 01:13:47.733
<i>because you have to remember
he was a marathon runner,</i>

01:13:47.757 --> 01:13:52.558
<i>you know he used to run 12 miles
every day and felt bad if he didn't</i>

01:13:52.637 --> 01:13:55.811
<i>and it was a spectacularly
big change of life for Frank</i>

01:13:55.890 --> 01:13:57.312
<i>when he had his accident.</i>

01:13:57.391 --> 01:14:00.315
So what, what kind
of music did you introduce him to?

01:14:00.394 --> 01:14:01.737
Bach.

01:14:01.812 --> 01:14:07.990
♪ Erbarme dich ♪
♪ Johann Sebastian Bach ♪

01:14:10.821 --> 01:14:14.041
<i>I mean I thought
that my pal Frank was indestructible,</i>

01:14:14.116 --> 01:14:15.834
<i>you know he got away with everything,</i>

01:14:15.910 --> 01:14:18.959
<i>Frank'll be alright
but he wasn't on this one</i>

01:14:19.038 --> 01:14:21.757
<i>and Pd go and see him
three or four times a week,</i>

01:14:21.832 --> 01:14:23.709
<i>I always gave him a kiss, I had to,</i>

01:14:23.793 --> 01:14:25.270
<i>lean over and give him a kiss
