<i>Frank Williams is wonderful</i>

01:25:11.982 --> 01:25:14.326
<i>and for all those years
Mum had been in the background,</i>

01:25:14.401 --> 01:25:16.449
<i>I don't think she did it,
she didn't wanna do it</i>

01:25:16.528 --> 01:25:18.155
<i>because she wanted fame or adulation,</i>

